{"tid":2492003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"用維基百科係咪好大鑊？","createTime":"2021-04-16T17:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T19:35:34.000Z","uid":142763,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0635383b0b8fd4eaeaaccd4d9b4fa91a51a3c686","tid":2492003,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"唔好負評住先，點解會咁問係因為其實維基百科其實有幾可靠？維基百科裏面有唔少嘅資料都冇reference。變咗對於資料有幾可靠（Reality)同埋<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">可供查證</span></span>(Verifiability)都係受都質疑。同埋有啲data都好多年前先update過，或者啲資料並唔係喺同一年出版，假如GDP PPP Per Capita <br />\n資料唔係喺同一年份出版，係咁嘅情況之下，相互嘅對比就未能夠反映實質嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">更大嘅問題係全世界所有人都可以刪改維基百科上嘅資料。</span></span>變咗有啲爭議性嘅條目，好容易加入咗個人意見，變咗唔夠中立。<br />\n<br />\n我咁樣講唔係叫大家唔好用維基百科，但係睇完最緊要fact check。或者用Britannica可能係一個更好嘅option。(利申：非Britannica打手)"},{"pid":"73f3d9424dcc0510f23929169e33a5ccce86b4a5","tid":2492003,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"我平時做project直接quote Wikipedia <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d488022d0dbf71e1ac72621f4c57289ee6686d99","tid":2492003,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"你意思係話伯母係女人？"},{"pid":"59d994a4e54e2f1360e90f55a174a48d55c38b04","tid":2492003,"uid":189235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"用維基quote過嘅reference 做reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d216066ed8be26e1aaad24ef1a9cdefd43bf943a","tid":2492003,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73f3d9424dcc0510f23929169e33a5ccce86b4a5","tid":2492003,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"我平時做project直接quote Wikipedia <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:56:16.000Z","msg":"最起碼quote wiki下面d ref啦<b